name: Exclusive Series TAA 2020
additionalNotes: The Tatuaje TAA 2020 is a 5 5/8" x 54 box-pressed parejo that includes a Nicaraguan binder, Nicaraguan fillers, and a Sumatran wrapper. This is the first time that Tatuaje has used a Sumatran wrapper in their TAA exclusive cigar. Limited to only 3,000 boxes of 20.
